text: Dave Jaumotte is a former American football player and coach. He served as the head football coach at Saint Francis University in Loretto, Pennsylvania from 1999 to 2001, compiling a record of 2–30. Prior to that, Jaumotte was an assistant coach in the Detroit Lions organization.
